{"tid":1134106,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Kevin Hart自導自演荷里活版《炸雞特攻隊》","createTime":"2019-05-01T14:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T22:26:26.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90866cf5326c4b493f5368dfb99072699fdf264e","tid":1134106,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"韓國爆笑動作喜劇片《炸雞特攻隊》今年年初上映成為熱話，票房收益累積逾9.3億港元，成為當地最收得電影，美國諧星Kevin Hart近日落實翻拍《炸雞》，更將自導自演，《Girls Trip》編劇Tracy Oliver負責改編劇本，電影公司現正進行選角階段。 <br />\n<br />\nKevin今次與韓國CJ娛樂一方合作翻拍電影，他亦有發聲明講及雙方的合作，更笑稱電影將是他成為韓星的踏腳石！Kevin現正翻拍英文版《陽光姊妹淘》，未知是否對韓片別有興趣？而《炸雞》一片當中有向港產片致敬元素，包括用上張國榮的音樂，未知翻拍英文版會否保留？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190501/photo/bkn-20190501103717103-0501_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190501185209\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190501103717103-0501_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190501185209&h=538f00ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d66e17a7ff3bd0b3e693eec9872ea590de150c2f","tid":1134106,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"KFC特攻隊？"},{"pid":"51e8f24e379b7ab99929bc1e4f899d6ec2a02661","tid":1134106,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d66e17a7ff3bd0b3e693eec9872ea590de150c2f","tid":1134106,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"KFC特攻隊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:05:35.000Z","msg":"中國版賣小龍蝦<br />\n韓國版賣炸雞<br />\n美國版應該賣pizza?"},{"pid":"7dfc5ca7316b06d323dfe9758adf21861a4822df","tid":1134106,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:26:26.000Z","msg":"炸雞特攻隊<br />\n好一般喎<br />\n咁都改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}